    • Method Detail

      • find

        public static KeyType find(String type,
           String mediaType,
           String extension)
        Searches for a parameter value that is defined as a static constant in this class.
        Parameters:
        type - the TYPE parameter value to search for (e.g. "PGP") or null to not search by this value
        mediaType - the media type to search for (e.g. "application/pgp-keys") or null to not search by this value
        extension - the file extension to search for (excluding the ".", e.g. "pgp") or null to not search by this value
        Returns:
        the object or null if not found

      • get

        public static KeyType get(String type,
          String mediaType,
          String extension)
        Searches for a parameter value and creates one if it cannot be found. All objects are guaranteed to be unique, so they can be compared with == equality.
        Parameters:
        type - the TYPE parameter value to search for (e.g. "PGP") or null to not search by this value
        mediaType - the media type to search for (e.g. "application/pgp-keys") or null to not search by this value
        extension - the file extension to search for (excluding the ".", e.g. "pgp") or null to not search by this value
        Returns:
        the object
